metadata.name: Crystal Ape #1
metadata.description: Public Mint is currently Live: https://www.crystalape.com. Become a Crystal Ape. As an CAYC member, you can own any of the 6,363 Crystal Apes, thoughtfully recreated into unique AI-generated Crystal Paintings. Only one painting will be minted for each Crystal Ape, and 24 distinct AI-models have been applied across the collection, to help create value for the owner of every individual ERC-721 token. Each mint of Crystal Ape Art will be eligible for future drops of specially designed frames to highlight your fine art.
